{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"122938-how-to-catch-the-wind","title":"How to Catch the Wind","description":"What do wings, kites and a wind turbine’s blades all have in common? Each one’s motion is powered by the wind.","language":"English","langCode":"en","isRtl":false,"level":"2","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Anjali Vaidya"],"illustrators":["Ivette Salom"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Pratham Books","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/122938-how-to-catch-the-wind"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/180153/size3/36c83df1c3a7270a1c44747a7358c3ff.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/180153/size6/36c83df1c3a7270a1c44747a7358c3ff.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/170849/size6/bd349faf216e90ede74af57a08628bfe.jpg","text":"Air is always around us.\nMoving air is called wind.\nWhen wind blows,\nit carries energy.","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/170851/size6/c0dd2ef1ed354630be32117bd6447cab.jpg","text":"The wind’s energy can\nlift kites into the sky.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/170852/size6/c9c47b1ea014f5b066e98521145ba0e9.jpg","text":"When something resists\nthe wind’s movement,\nits energy can build up...","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/170854/size6/4d338c4a44369ac93b4a871285ddbea3.jpg","text":"before releasing in a violent burst.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/170855/size6/6efc70d79a7c66c4cf849d1b23569dbb.jpg","text":"But we can also capture the wind’s energy\nand change it into energy that we can use.","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/170856/size6/f0f890adc6fd9bdcb7cb54971435436e.jpg","text":"Turbines help us transform\nwind energy into electrical energy.\nThe energy of moving air makes\nthe blades of a wind turbine spin.","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/170857/size6/00410773d87506e94596e1a28472a0fd.jpg","text":"And the spinning blades change\nwind energy into electricity.","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/170858/size6/3fa2f92dd2ae00599bb8e94c740f1fe9.jpg","text":"We can use this electricity\nlong after the wind stops blowing.","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":8,"words":101}}